title: Is Anybody Up?
itunes:title: Is Anybody Up?
description:
The homies from No Ceiling's podcast, Glasses Malone & Peter stop by and we talk about Netflix doc, "The Most Hated Man On The Internet". Sociopath, Hunter Moore, who made it his mission to embarrass as many people as he could by posting their nude photo's on his now defunct site, isanybodyup.com wound up getting locked up and banned from the internet.  We also check in real quick with the homie 40 Glock
